  "description": "Dropout is a regularization technique for reducing overfitting by preventing neuron co-adaption during training as described in the paper:Improving neural networks by preventing co-adaptation of feature detectorsThe dropout operator randomly sets the outputs of some units to zero, while upscale others according to the given dropout probability.",
